description:
Britney Spears CoverArt is a new 'Exhibition' app that allows you to visulize an artists discography in a cool new way!
With Britney Spears CoverArt you'll never be without Britney! Album Covers from "..oops i did it again" to her newest album "femme fatale," and her comeback album "Circus," will slide across your screen while lyrics flow beneath! CoverSlide - Britney Spears is the perfect app for any Britney fan! *note: app should not be opened from launcher, open using the 'exhibition' app*
